{"tid":1144682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［年經］落大雨都唔帶摭都唔知係咩居心？","createTime":"2019-05-08T08:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T10:35:49.000Z","uid":142824,"like":25,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7ff0ac8cd7e7e2a18f5203a1361c7836ea1f42","tid":1144682,"uid":142824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"過雲雨我都算啦<br />\n落咗幾日大雨都唔撚識帶摭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦我當你一時唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁唔該無帶摭就同我縮翻個龜頭入去咪撚企喺門口啦屌你</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次鳩次都有啲撚樣冇帶摭就企係地鐵站商場門口<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你唔係以為等等下會停雨啊嘛？？？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁撚On9唔怪得連摭都唔撚識帶啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171ca07217bccababd1e0100d9d364c3b4148934","tid":1144682,"uid":57928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:22:48.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"42ad0d2bc43117c59b740631552eb623e0592901","tid":1144682,"uid":126690,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5328e63a4d8edf8b7b217190f4d528618c67acea","tid":1144682,"uid":142824,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"屌你我可能真係要年年都要出post屌鳩柒呢班撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且好似仲有年輕化趨勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心學就唔好學啲廢老醒少少唔好叫人打攪伯母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊post:<br />\n無帶遮就麻煩入返去地鐵站啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/752909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/752909</